description: I. Refusals at initial decision on asylum applications, humanitarian protection and discretionary leave in the UK from Jan 2007 to June 2009. 3 p. II. Tables showing removals and voluntary departures of principal asylum cases from Jan 2007 to June 2009 for Afghanistan; Belarus; Myanmar; China; Colombia; Cuba; Democratic Republic of the Congo; North Korea; Iran; Iraq; Israell; occupied Palestinian territory; Pakistan; Russia; Saudi Arabia; Somalia; Sudan; Syria; Turkmenistan; Uzbekistan; Vietnam and Zimbabwe. 22 p.
